[{"id":"e6d96758db682947907ed988aea9b8e0","from":"Aereo","from_email":"email@email.aereo.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Let\u2019s Raise Our Voices","date":"2014-07-01T13:42:47.000Z","formatted_date":"Jul 1, 2014","formatted_time":"1:42 PM","body":"To view this email as a web page, go to the link below, or copy and paste it into your browser's address window.\nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db872a7fde7eb21a31c6f8ac691299077670bb27889cf49326\nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db04b9ec51152a44b816733c5da1ca4e31e449db4105421d32 \n\n\nA Letter to Our Consumers: Standing Together for Innovation, Progress and Technology - Let's Raise Our Voices\n\n\nOn Saturday, many of you received the news that we decided to pause our operations temporarily, as a result of the United States Supreme Court's reversal of a lower court decision in favor of Aereo.\n\n\n\nYour response in support of the Aereo team has been overwhelming and touching. Your tweets, emails and Facebook posts have made it clear how important it is for so many Americans to have access to a cloud-based antenna to watch live broadcast television. Many of you have asked, \"What can we do?\" \n\n\n\nToday, I'm asking you to raise your hands and make your voices heard. Tell your lawmakers how disappointed you are that the nation's highest court issued a decision that could deny you the right to use the antenna of your choice to access live over-the-air broadcast television. Tell them your stories of why having access to a cloud-based antenna is important to you and your families. Show them you care about this issue. \n\n\n\nVisit the updated \nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db404ed5277368aae564260842fd09576c240a1696b92c80ba \nProtectMyAntenna.org , find your representatives and send tweets, emails and Facebook messages asking them to take action to protect your right to use the antenna of your choice to access live free-to-air broadcasts, including the ability to use a cloud-based antenna.\n\n\n\nDon't let your voices be silenced. Let's stand together for innovation, progress, and technology.\n\n\n\nThank you for your continued support. We are truly grateful.\n\n\n\nYours truly,\n\n\nChet Kanojia\n\n\nFounder & CEO\n\nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db0e4a08f2da7958d1e83fd5e70bc8ef060d3f1640beac4e3d \nTerms of Use \n  |  \nPrivacy Policy \n\n  |  \n\nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db5a3960694c3d82920d7e7ba0c0a887363eba395ea6d05165 \nSupported Devices \n\nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db09a3cb4e5ec636ff032e55d7324769d850c78bdf6a8cf266 \n\n   \nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1dbe24b40d2d18061e55dd4a177ba531d3477828e7492eda89e \n\n   \nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1dbf6b728cc90cf0566b2b6ce5019cb026ae3e99d81aba67c89 \n\n   \nhttp://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db81c3d5c7adb9743e2733d3b771688c7b92f2aa896fb41221 \n\nCopyright (c) 2014 Aereo, Inc.\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------\n\t\n\tThis email was sent by:\n\tAereo, Inc\n\t455 Broadway, 4th Fl\n\tNew York, NY, 10013, \n\t\n\tWe respect your right to privacy - visit the following URL to view our policy.\n\t( http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db4e7a8c228465d994e253dc171cc00fd977b8543487beffca )\n\t\n\t----------------------------------------\n\t\n\tVisit the following URL to manage your subscriptions.\n\t( http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1dbb2f71c063a25027c64c9d1e30664a92bb97cefea6326d4b8 )\n\t\n\tVisit the following URL to update your profile.\n\t( http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db14180d7d92fb68777b95cc567232338cd0ba5f94707374f2 )\n\t\n\tVisit the following URL to unsubscribe.\n\t( http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db2bb1db943d5f00cd41d09aae594534f4b8dc8ed2c4ec7ee1 )\n\t\n","body_html":"<HTML><body><style type=\"text/css\">\ndiv.preheader \n{ display: none !important; } \n</style>\n<div class=\"preheader\" style=\"font-size: 1px; display: none !important;\">On Saturday, many of you received the news that we decided to pause our operations temporarily</div><P><center><table width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" id=\"header_table\"> <tr> <td width=\"100%\" align=\"center\"> <font face=\"verdana\" size=\"1\" color=\"#444444\"> To view this email as a web page, go <a href=\"http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db5e54a9a9e7dd2bef199ea3686628c29b0dfe8ac802edfa56\" > here.</a><br> </font> </td> </tr> </table> </center></P>\n<img src=\"http://click.email.aereo.com/open.aspx?ffcb10-fec315777763007a-fe2d10727365017e751376-fe8a127171630d7f7d-fef91675716201-fe83117273620c747d-ffcf14\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n/* Mobile-specific Styles */\n@media only screen and (max-width: 660px) { \n/* Custom Styles for ET */\n#table5 { width: 300px; }\n#header_table { width: 300px; }\n/* End of Custom Styles for ET */\ntable[class=w30], td[class=w30], img[class=w30] { width:10px !important; }\ntable[class=w640], td[class=w640], img[class=w640] { width:280px !important; }\ntable[class=w700], td[class=w700], img[class=w700] { width:300px !important; min-width: 300px !important; }\n.article-content, #left-sidebar{ -webkit-text-size-adjust: 90% !important; -ms-text-size-adjust: 90% !important; }\n.header-content, .footer-content-left {-webkit-text-size-adjust: 80% !important; -ms-text-size-adjust: 80% !important;}\nimg { /*width: auto !important;*/ height: auto!important; line-height: 100%; max-width: 100% !important;}\n } \n/* Client-specific Styles */\n#outlook a { padding: 0; }  /* Force Outlook to provide a \"view in browser\" button. */\nbody { width: 100% !important; }\n.ReadMsgBody { width: 100%; }\n.ExternalClass { width: 100%; display:block !important; } /* Force Hotmail to display emails at full width */\n/* Reset Styles */\n/* Add 100px so mobile switch bar doesn't cover street address. */\nbody { background-color: #ececec; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\nimg { outline: none; text-decoration: none; display: inline;}\na {color: #3db4ba; text-decoration: underline;}\nbr, strong br, b br, em br, i br { line-height:100%; }\nh1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { line-height: 100% !important; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }\ntable td, table tr { border-collapse: collapse; }\n.yshortcuts, .yshortcuts a, .yshortcuts a:link,.yshortcuts a:visited, .yshortcuts a:hover, .yshortcuts a span {\ncolor: black; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom: none !important; background: none !important;\n}   /* Body text color for the New Yahoo.  This example sets the font of Yahoo's Shortcuts to black. */\n/* This most probably won't work in all email clients. Don't include code blocks in email. */\ncode {\n  white-space: normal;\n  word-break: break-all;\n}\n/*#background-table { background-color: #666666; margin: 10px; }*/\n/* Webkit Elements */\n#footer { -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }\n/* Fonts and Content */\nbody, td { font-family: HelveticaNeue, sans-serif; }\n\n/* Prevent Webkit and Windows Mobile platforms from changing default font sizes on header and footer. */\n.article-content { font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-family: HelveticaNeue, sans-serif; }\n.article-content img { max-width: 100% }\n.article-content ol, .article-content ul { margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:18px; margin-left:19px; padding:0; }\n.article-content li { font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; }\n.article-content p {margin-bottom: 15px;}\n/*#footer { background-color: #666666; color: #fff; }*/ \n#footer { background-color: #666666; color: #fff; } \n#footer a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }\n#footer img { display: inline !important;}\n</style>\n<!--[if gte mso 9]>\n<style _tmplitem=\"33\" >\n.article-content ol, .article-content ul {\n   margin: 0 0 0 24px;\n   padding: 0;\n   list-style-position: inside;\n}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n\n        <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" id=\"background-table\">\n            <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                    <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ececec\">\n                        <table class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                            <tbody>                               \n                                <tr>\n                                    <td id=\"header\" class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n                              <table class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                                <tbody>\n                                 <tr>\n                                   <td width=\"700\" class=\"w700\" style=\"min-width: 700px;\">\n                                  <div align=\"center\" id=\"headline\">     \n                                    <div style=\"padding: 10px; background-color: #666666;\">\n<a href=\"http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db8b1e97f005b0cc543e8853cbca39e7c711c689bbcd5f8dea\" title=\"Aereo\"  ><img width=\"142\" height=\"38\" border=\"0\" title=\"Aereo\" src=\"http://image.email.aereo.com/lib/fe8a127171630d7f7d/m/1/logo_aereo_padding.png\" id=\"image-placeholder\" alt=\"Aereo\" style=\"width: 142px; height: 38px; border-color: #000000; margin: 0px;\" thid=\"f8213124-aa49-42ab-92ee-f6b08a46896b\" /></a>\n</div>                   \n                                  </div>\n                                   </td>\n                                 </tr>\n                                </tbody>\n                              </table>\n\n                            </td>\n                                </tr>                               \n                                <tr id=\"simple-content-row\"><td class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n                                  <br />\n                                    <table class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                                        <tbody>\n                                            <tr>\n                                                <td class=\"w30\" width=\"30\"></td>\n                                                <td class=\"w640\" width=\"640\">\n                                                    <table class=\"w640\" width=\"640\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                                                        <tbody>\n                                                            <tr>\n                                                                <td class=\"w640\" width=\"640\">                            \n                                                                    <div align=\"left\" class=\"article-content\">                                                                      \n                                                                        <h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">\nA Letter to Our Consumers: Standing Together for Innovation, Progress and Technology - Let's Raise Our Voices\n</h1>\n\n<img width=\"300\" height=\"205\" border=\"0\" align=\"right\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 205px; border-color: #ffffff; margin: 0px 10px 10px;\" alt=\"Photo of Chet Kanojia\" title=\"Photo of Chet Kanojia\" src=\"http://image.email.aereo.com/lib/fe8a127171630d7f7d/m/1/chet_320x219.jpg\" thid=\"0c9fc99e-3933-42af-8241-afff57920801\" />\n\n<p>\nOn Saturday, many of you received the news that we decided to pause our operations temporarily, as a result of the United States Supreme Court's reversal of a lower court decision in favor of Aereo.  \n</p>\n\n<p>\nYour response in support of the Aereo team has been overwhelming and touching. Your tweets, emails and Facebook posts have made it clear how important it is for so many Americans to have access to a cloud-based antenna to watch live broadcast television. Many of you have asked, \"What can we do?\" \n</p>\n\n<p>\nToday, I'm asking you to raise your hands and make your voices heard. Tell your lawmakers how disappointed you are that the nation's highest court issued a decision that could deny you the right to use the antenna of your choice to access live over-the-air broadcast television. Tell them your stories of why having access to a cloud-based antenna is important to you and your families. Show them you care about this issue. \n</p>\n\n<p>\nVisit the updated <a href=\"http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db404ed5277368aae564260842fd09576c240a1696b92c80ba\">ProtectMyAntenna.org</a>, find your representatives and send tweets, emails and Facebook messages asking them to take action to protect your right to use the antenna of your choice to access live free-to-air broadcasts, including the ability to use a cloud-based antenna.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nDon't let your voices be silenced. Let's stand together for innovation, progress, and technology.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nThank you for your continued support. We are truly grateful.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nYours truly,<br />\n<img width=\"180\" height=\"69\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Chet Kanojia\" title=\"Chet Kanojia\" src=\"http://image.email.aereo.com/lib/fe8a127171630d7f7d/m/1/ceo-signature.jpg\" style=\"width: 180px; height: 69px; border-color: #000000; margin: 0px;\" />\n<br />\nChet Kanojia<br /></p>\nFounder & CEO\n                                                                    </div>\n                                                                </td>\n                                                            </tr>\n                                                            <tr>\n                                                                <td class=\"w640\" width=\"640\" height=\"10\"></td>\n                                                            </tr>\n                                                        </tbody>\n                                                    </table>\n                                                </td>\n                                                <td class=\"w30\" width=\"30\"></td>\n                                            </tr>\n                                        </tbody>\n                                    </table>\n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" height=\"15\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\"></td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"w700\" width=\"700\">\n\n                                    <!-- <table id=\"footer\" class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#666666\"> -->\n                                    <table id=\"footer\" class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#666666\">\n                                        <tbody>\n                                            <tr>\n                                                <td colspan=\"3\" class=\"w700\" width=\"700\" height=\"30\"></td>\n                                            </tr>\n                                            <tr>\n                                                <td class=\"w30\" width=\"30\"></td>\n                                                <td class=\"w640\" width=\"640\" valign=\"top\">\n                                                    <span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: white;\">\n                                                        <a style=\"color:#ffffff; font-size:13px;\" href=\"http://click.email.aereo.com/?qs=296e41411f85d1db0e4a08f2da7958d1e83fd5e70bc8ef060d3f1640beac4e3d\">Terms of Use</a>\n                                                        &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;\n         